e 500W Bafang motor delivers up to 28 mph of assist. Torque + cadence sensors adjust power naturally to your effort, so the ride feels steady and intuitive, not jerky. Use the left-hand thumb throttle when you want a boost.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_7CfGCR","text_L7Xexj"],"name":"Image with text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/cityrobinX_closeup.png","image_width":700,"image_link":"","image_position":"right","text_alignment":"left","color_scheme":"default"}},"image_with_text_LVGfkP":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_dct86R":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Comfort You Can Feel From the First Ride","use_h1":true}},"text_4i34W7":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Built for riders who want to sit upright, relax their shoulders, and keep pressure off wrists and knees. <\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_dct86R","text_4i34W7"],"name":"Image with text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/dan.gif","image_width":700,"image_link":"","image_position":"right","text_alignment":"left","color_scheme":"default"}},"multi_column_9QLj7H":{"type":"multi-column","blocks":{"text_block_b4BnMX":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CityRobinX_FrontSuspension.png","title":"SR Suntour Front Suspension","text":"<p>With 100mm of travel and preload + lockout adjustment, the SR Suntour fork smooths out bumps for a steady, comfortable ride on city streets or trails.”<\/p>","button_label":"","link":""}},"text_block_jPah8z":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CityRobinX_SeatpostSuspension.png","title":"Cushioned Seat Comfort","text":"<p>Our Velo Plush saddle and SR Suntour NCX suspension seatpost work together to cushion every bump, so even long rides stay easy on your body.<\/p>","button_label":"","link":""}},"text_block_ATzkUB":{"type":"text_block","disabled":true,"settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/stepthru1.svg","title":"Safety Verified","text":"<p>SGS certified to UL 2271 and UL 2849.<\/p>","button_label":"","link":""}}},"block_order":["text_block_b4BnMX","text_block_jPah8z","text_block_ATzkUB"],"name":"Multi-column","settings":{"title":"Smooth on Every Road","media_aspect_ratio":"s","media_width":700,"text_alignment":"center","button_style":"primary","color_scheme":"default"}},"image_with_text_yA7C4k":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_NWMQ7b":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Ride with Confidence","use_h1":true}},"subheading_qEpj9c":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"— SGS Certified"}},"text_inb4bq":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Every City Robin X+ is SGS certified in line with UL 2271 & UL 2849 standards. From battery durability to electrical protection, every detail is third-party tested for your safety. Add in Tektro hydraulic brakes, Schwalbe Super Moto X tires, and integrated brake lights, and you’ve got stopping power and visibility you can trust.<\/p>","enlarge_text":true}}},"block_order":["heading_NWMQ7b","subheading_qEpj9c","text_inb4bq"],"name":"Image with text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/City_Robin_X_Rear_Lighting_Detail.png","image_width":700,"image_link":"","image_position":"left","text_alignment":"left","color_scheme":"default"}},"logo_list_YYzANP":{"type":"logo-list","blocks":{"logo_6pWFEg":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/range.svg","image_width":100,"link":"","title":"Up to 60 miles per charge"}},"logo_DppPNc":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Speed.svg","image_width":100,"link":"","title":"28 mph top speed (Class 3 compliant)"}},"logo_4yJ3Fk":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/mph.svg","image_width":100,"link":"","title":"Custom 48V\/20A controller"}}},"block_order":["logo_6pWFEg","logo_DppPNc","logo_4yJ3Fk"],"disabled":true,"name":"Logo list","settings":{"title":"Commute or Cruise with Confidence","image_opacity":75,"color_scheme":"default"}},"image_with_text_overlay_XpLVF9":{"type":"image-with-text-overlay","blocks":{"heading_Tf4pQY":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Easy to Control","heading_max_width":15,"title_size":84,"title_size_mobile":32,"use_h1":false}},"text_cCX6TL":{"type":"text","disabled":true,"settings":{"text":"<p>Color LCD shows speed and battery at a glance. Use the thumb throttle when you want a boost. No app required and no account needed.<\/p>","enlarge_text":true}}},"block_order":["heading_Tf4pQY","text_cCX6TL"],"disabled":true,"name":"Image with text overlay","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/cityrobinX_displayscreen.png","height":"adapt","height_desktop":600,"height_mobile":460,"image_link":"","full_width":true,"text_alignment":"bottom left","mobile_overlay_under":true,"overlay_style":"box"}},"image_with_text_HyyrHB":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_zEtFKh":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Total Privacy","use_h1":true}},"text_dhNJFW":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Easy to control with a left-side color LCD showing your speed and battery. Use the thumb throttle for extra help when you want it. Your ride, your privacy. Euphree is American owned and never tracks you.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_zEtFKh","text_dhNJFW"],"name":"Image with text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/City_Robin_X_Cockpit_and_Handlebars_cf077e6c-289f-4c1d-ab57-e45a566c048d.png","image_width":700,"image_link":"","image_position":"right","text_alignment":"left","color_scheme":"default"}},"image_with_text_kw4mhY":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_YDUDR9":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Patented Hidden Wiring","use_h1":true}},"text_mxyM94":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Clean, protected, easy to service. Our integrated hidden wiring is patented and pioneered by Euphree to keep your cockpit neat and your electronics shielded.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_YDUDR9","text_mxyM94"],"disabled":true,"name":"Image with text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/cityrobinx_frontfork.png","image_width":700,"image_link":"","image_position":"left","text_alignment":"left","color_scheme":"default"}},"image_with_text_zCzY8V":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_bYFFAE":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Trusted Name-Brand Components","use_h1":true}},"text_eMWHa3":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>LG batteries, Shimano shifting, Tektro brakes, Schwalbe tires. Parts mechanics know and keep in stock.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_bYFFAE","text_eMWHa3"],"disabled":true,"name":"Image with text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/cityrobinX_closeup.png","image_width":700,"image_link":"","image_position":"left","text_alignment":"left","color_scheme":"default"}},"multi_column_prhDxA":{"type":"multi-column","blocks":{"text_block_cM9XVb":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CityRobinX_CafeLock.png","title":"Cafe Lock","text":"","button_label":"","link":""}},"text_block_aMpGM7":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/cityrobinx_frontfork.png","title":"Metal Fenders","text":"","button_label":"","link":""}},"text_block_HFmJY7":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/City_Robin_X_rear_light.png","title":"Rear Light","text":"","button_label":"","link":""}}},"block_order":["text_block_cM9XVb","text_block_aMpGM7","text_block_HFmJY7"],"disabled":true,"name":"Multi-column","settings":{"title":"Integrated Lock, Full Fenders, Bright Lights","media_aspect_ratio":"s","media_width":700,"text_alignment":"center","button_style":"primary","color_scheme":"default"}},"background_video_UJNddM":{"type":"background-video","name":"Background video","settings":{"video_shopify":"shopify:\/\/files\/videos\/X+closeups.mp4","video_external":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc","video_description":"","text_alignment":"center center","height_desktop":600,"height_mobile":500,"full_width":true,"overlay_style":"full image-overlay--bg-shadow"}},"collapsible_tabs_V4Qpmr":{"type":"collapsible-tabs","blocks":{"question_3eTFpp":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Comfort & Safety","answer":"<ul><li><strong>Step-through aluminum frame (6061 alloy)<\/strong> for easy on and off<\/li><li><strong>Suspension seatpost (SR Suntour NCX)<\/strong> absorbs bumps and reduces strain<\/li><li><strong>Front suspension fork (SR Suntour XCM 32, 100mm travel)<\/strong> for smooth handling on city streets and trails<\/li><li><strong>Velo wide comfort saddle<\/strong> designed for upright, relaxed riding<\/li><li><strong>Front & rear integrated lights with brake signal<\/strong> for visibility day or night<\/li><li><strong>Integrated café lock<\/strong> lets you secure your bike quickly when parked<\/li><\/ul>"}},"question_kFeJhf":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Practical Features","answer":"<ul><li><strong>Welded-in rear rack<\/strong> (100 lb capacity) for cargo, panniers, or baskets<\/li><li><strong>Full fenders<\/strong> to keep you clean and dry<\/li><li><strong>USB-C charging port<\/strong> for powering your phone or accessories<\/li><li><strong>Double-walled rims & Schwalbe Super Moto X 27.5” x 2.4” tires<\/strong> for puncture resistance and stability<\/li><\/ul>"}},"question_NqW8RB":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Drivetrain & Brakes","answer":"<ul><li><strong>Shimano Altus 7-speed derailleur<\/strong> with 11–28T gearing<\/li><li><strong>Aluminum alloy crankset (170mm) + KMC Z7 stainless steel chain<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Tektro E350 hydraulic disc brakes with 180mm rotors (front & rear)<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Adjustable brake levers with motor cutoff<\/strong> for safe stopping<\/li><\/ul>"}},"question_47dcDN":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Electronics","answer":"<ul><li><strong>Battery:<\/strong> 48V, 14Ah (672Wh) Samsung\/LG cells, removable<\/li><li><strong>Controller:<\/strong> Custom in-frame, 48V 20A<\/li><li><strong>Display:<\/strong> Left-mounted color LCD, easy to read<\/li><li><strong>Headlight:<\/strong> 200-lumen dual beam LED<\/li><li><strong>Rear light:<\/strong> Integrated with brake signal, 220° visibility<\/li><li><strong>Charger:<\/strong> 48V, 3A fast charger (included)<\/li><\/ul>"}},"question_ynJEAP":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Sizing & Geometry","answer":"<p>Designed to fit riders <strong>5’2” – 6’0”<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>Seat Height:<\/strong> 33” – 40” (min–max)<\/li><li><strong>Handlebar Height:<\/strong> 42” – 45” adjustable<\/li><li><strong>Standover Height:<\/strong> 17”<\/li><li><strong>Seat Tube Length:<\/strong> 15”<\/li><li><strong>Reach:<\/strong> 16”<\/li><li><strong>Top Tube Length:<\/strong> 23”<\/li><li><strong>Wheelbase:<\/strong> 46”<\/li><li><strong>Total Length:<\/strong> 72”<\/li><\/ul>"}},"question_PiPAYV":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Weight & Capacity","answer":"<ul><li><strong>Bike Weight:<\/strong> 64 lbs<\/li><li><strong>Total Payload Capacity:<\/strong> 350 lbs<\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["question_3eTFpp","question_kFeJhf","question_NqW8RB","question_47dcDN","question_ynJEAP","question_PiPAYV"],"name":"Collapsible tabs","settings":{"title":"Technical Specifications"}},"collapsible_tabs_iHqyR9":{"type":"collapsible-tabs","blocks":{"question_VniTKh":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Drivetrain","answer":"<ul><li>8-speed Shimano Altus with 13–32T freewheel<\/li><li>KMC anti-rust chain<\/li><li>170 mm alloy crank, 50–52T chainring<\/li><\/ul>"}},"question_wKkcKe":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Frame & cargo","answer":"<ul><li>6061 aluminum step-through frame<\/li><li>Welded rear rack, 50 lb capacity<\/li><li>Full-coverage aluminum fenders<\/li><\/ul>"}},"question_eHiGdR":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Suspension & wheelset","answe